  "text": "Quality control of the reads was done with the software FastQC version 0.11.2 (Andrews 2010). The short reads were mapped to version 9 of the Danio rerio genome using the splice aware aligner Star version 2.3.1o [CITATION_1] using the ensemble gene models to facilitate efficient mapping of spliced reads.",
